data.description: Come tour this country oasis just 10 minutes south of Lake Gaston! Newly constructed in 2022, this custom home is surrounded by 10 acres of open land, riding trails, scenic woods, private outdoor shooting range and more. A real sportspersons paradise awaits.  Inside you will find the finer touches of modern design mixed with a country farmhouse feel. Your kitchen is complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas stove, center island, large pantry and recessed lighting. The spacious primary bedroom is adjoined with a double vanity sink and large ceramic tiled shower. Recently installed LVP flooring throughout brings an inviting feel to the living room with a gas fireplace with open dining and kitchen area. The three car garage comes with an E/V charge on site. This may be great opportunity for vacation rental property!
